<main class="recipe-content">
  <img src="../images/pasta.jpg" alt="Creamy Pasta" class="recipe-img">
  <h2>Ingredients</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>200g pasta</li>
    <li>1 cup cream</li>
    <li>2 cloves garlic</li>
    <li>Olive oil, salt, pepper</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Instructions</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Boil pasta until al dente.</li>
    <li>Sauté garlic in olive oil.</li>
    <li>Add cream, salt, pepper, and simmer.</li>
    <li>Toss pasta into the sauce and serve warm.</li>
  </ol>
</main>

